name: Gemini 2.0 Pro Experimental (02-05)
description: Experimental snapshot (February 5, 2025) of best-in-class Gemini model for coding and complex prompts. Supports 2M token context and advanced tool use including code execution and search.
notes: EXPERIMENTAL - Free via Google AI Studio and Vertex AI. Released February 5, 2025. Strongest coding performance of any Gemini model. 50% improvement on SimpleQA benchmark over 2.0 Flash. Supports advanced tool calling including Google Search and code execution. Available in Gemini app for Advanced users.
